  "title": "Mildly Peppery Saudi Arabian Cucumber Salad",
  "description": "A refreshing and peppery Saudi Arabian salad featuring Persian cucumbers, perfect for a light brunch, and friendly to sugar-free diets.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
