  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine the sashimi-cut Persian cucumbers, chopped fresh mint leaves, and chopped fresh dill.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice, olive oil, minced garlic, black pepper, and salt to make the dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the cucumber mixture and toss to coat.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Just before serving, give the salad a good stir and adjust the seasoning if needed.",
    "Serve the salad chilled, garnished with additional mint leaves if desired."
